    "Despite efforts to cast a wide net by including multiple databases and outlets, the possibility of missing noteworthy papers remains.",
    "The selection and extraction process, which was guided by specific criteria, nevertheless retained elements of subjectivity.",
    "In addition, the quality and relevance of the literature serve as inherent limitations.",
